    "title": "Extremely slow Clang + Valgrind on macOS x86_64",
    "body": "The [\"x86_64: macOS Ventura, Valgrind (clang)\"](https://github.com/bitcoin-core/secp256k1/blob/f44c1ebd96b07a0431e476c85e921da56222f555/.github/workflows/ci.yml#L452) CI job takes more than 40 min:\n- https://github.com/bitcoin-core/secp256k1/actions/runs/18495253559/job/52697859721\n- https://github.com/bitcoin-core/secp256k1/actions/runs/18507649867/job/52740457457\n\nHowever, [\"x86_64: macOS Ventura, Valgrind (gcc)\"](https://github.com/bitcoin-core/secp256k1/blob/f44c1ebd96b07a0431e476c85e921da56222f555/.github/workflows/ci.yml#L453) takes less than 20 min:\n- https://github.com/bitcoin-core/secp256k1/actions/runs/18495253559/job/52697859732\n- https://github.com/bitcoin-core/secp256k1/actions/runs/18507649867/job/52740457434",
